              </div>
              <div>
                <h6 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">Ravi K.</h6>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Senior Recruiter, IT Services Firm</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-base flex-1">"Our whole team collaborates better. I can easily share AI reports with hiring managers and finalize decisions without long meetings. It keeps us aligned and fast."</p>
